snippet.title: Quake Champions – Ruins of Sarnath Arena Trailer
snippet.description:
The Ruins of Sarnath is currently playable in the Quake Champions Closed Beta. Signups are still open, so come join us in the Arena: https://beth.games/2oYzJpu

Time weighs heavy on the Ruins of Sarnath and nature has taken hold, dripping verdant greens into the wreckage of this ancient temple. Now, untold ages after they rose from the inky blackness of the Dreamlands, the Ruins of Sarnath are a blood-soaked killing field where Champions from the waking world fight to the death. 

Follow Quake Champions on social media:
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/quake
Twitter: http://twitter.com/quake
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/quake
